Zm_toxic_v2b125 - by krassell

Second version and 125th build of zm_toxic. 
Beta version - Fully playable but some bugs are possible. Write here all bugs you found in my map.
Map is very small, there only are a few camping spots. I warned you, so dont whine.

History:

Survivors broke in the old abandoned facility in search of shelter but zombie madness aleady was there and infection starts it's bloody journey from dead to living.

Gameplay:
Gameplay includes some unique things like healing machine and fire that can ignite player. Use them wisely! I tried to do no spots with one way in.

Extra area: It is very secret, most clever will find tips.

Other:
Actually it is my first serious project/release for CS:S so be nice.
All found bugs you can post here.
I think i paked all textures in bsp. if you got any textures missed post here.
I would to thank S-LoW for nice alien skin

This map is a remake from CS 1.6. I did it as realisticly as i could, I also added some secrets and a basement. Anybody who has played counter-strike 1.6 on a zombie server will undoubtebly remember this map to it's very detail. i've spent a lot of my time on it to make it good and playable. Map: zm_toxic_factory_v1
by: whisky
------------------------

Info:

The players are in a factory specialised in breaking down biohazard
materials, the workers all died after attacks from zombies,
your goal to stay alive as long as possible.

The map has alot to offer, such as 2 bunkers with 4 chambers in both, 
an outside area to run away from the zombies,inside the factory with 
some hiding places, and a cellar with toxic waste.
any way you should try it out :) it has some fun secrets to discover!

EDIT #1: Working on a better and more optimized version. It seems that 64+ player servers will experience FPS lag when on the tower. New version will be uploaded when it is fully tested on a 64 man server.

Changelog:
+ Removed a lot of the railing brushwork which was causing fps lag.
+ Broke up func_detail brush work so it wasn't one huge func_detail.
+ Added a lot of hint/skip and removed some unnecessary areaportals.
+ Removed some excessive lighting.

Original Post: I love the classic zm_towers but I decided it needed a face lift and this is the result. Please let me know your thoughts! :) Thanks!
